      "text_excerpt": "Accuride\ncustomer service\n888-491-7112\nFacebook\nTwitter\nInstagram\nWe Design & Manufacture Innovative Movement Solutions\nAPPLIANCES\nAUTOMATION & MACHINERY\nAUTOMOTIVE/ EV INTERIORS\nCOMMERCIAL KITCHENS\nCLOUD/AI SERVER\nContact our Solutions Specialist\n888-491-7112\nCUSTOM OEM SOLUTIONS\nLEARN MORE\nLATEST BLOGS\nREAD MORE\nCASE STUDIES\nREAD MORE"
