    "products": {
      "url": "https://www.accuride.com/products",
      "text": "Learn More About Accuride Products | Quality, Variety & Dependability\nAccuride\ncustomer service\n888-491-7112\nFacebook\nTwitter\nInstagram\nProducts\nExplore the variety of movement solutions and accessories we offer to propel your project forward and enhance your application’s design.\nTo narrow down your search, you can choose a category below.\nDrawer slides\nAccuride specializes in the global manufacturing of high-quality, custom drawer slides. From light-duty to heavy- and even super-duty, you are guaranteed to find a movement solution that not only complements but also elevates your design.\nLight, Medium and Heavy Duty Slides\nLEARN MORE\nLIGHT DUTY\nFor lighter applications, our light-duty sliding solutions bring better performance and reliability to any application with a maximum load rating of 140 lbs.\nLearn More\nMEDIUM DUTY\nKnown around the world for their versatility, our medium-duty drawer slides bear loads from 140 lbs. - 170 lbs.\nLearn More\nHEAVY DUTY\nDesigned for more robust applications, our heavy-duty drawer slides are built to withstand loads ranging from 170 lbs. - 600 lbs.\nLearn More\nSUPER HEAVY DUTY\nBuilt to withstand the toughest environments, our super heavy-duty drawer slides have load ratings over 600 lbs.\nLearn More\nSPECIALTY SLIDES\nFor more distinct and exclusive applications, we wield our engineering expertise to create movement solutions that transcend conventional drawer slides and workstations. Two-Way Travel, Linear Track Systems, Flipper & Pocket door Slides, Media Access, Keyboard Systems, Tilt-Track System, Pocket & Bayonet and Corrosion-Resistant Slides.\nLearn More\nELECTRONIC ENCLOSURE SLIDES\nWe offer many sliding solutions for 1U to 8U chassis. Our solutions include narrow side-space, over-travel (for easier access), locking mechanisms, disconnects, and adjustable bracket mounting.\nLearn More\nACCESS CONTROL\nOur access control products are designated for commercial drawer and door applications. Accuride’s access control systems are easy to use, install, and program--built to last even in the most demanding commercial environments.\nLearn More\nACCESSORIES\nBrowse some of Accuride’s additional accessories to give your application that extra push towards perfection.\nLearn More\nSTORE\nFeel ready to start browsing and adding Accuride products to your shopping cart? Visit our online store, try our trusty Slide Selector tool, search through our distribution partners, or check out our OEM custom program to find the movement solution that brings your application one step closer to completion.\nShop More"
    },
